研究中让它“复活”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/they-froze-a-brain-to-%e2%88%92196c-then-brought-it-back-to-life-in-a-groundbreaking-new-study</link><description>人类冬眠看似纯粹的科幻小说，但它可以使星际旅行成为现实。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/they-froze-a-brain-to-e28892196c-then-brought-it-back-to-life-in-a-groundbreaking-new-study.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 00:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/they-froze-a-brain-to-%e2%88%92196c-then-brought-it-back-to-life-in-a-groundbreaking-new-study</guid></item><item><title>为什么被丢弃的大脑“噪音”很重要：被忽视的网络可能会重塑心理健康治疗</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/why-discarded-brain-noise-matters-overlooked-networks-may-reshape-mental-health-treatment</link><description>使用成像来了解大脑复杂性的科学家经常关注最强的信号而忽略其余的信号。但研究人员警告说，这一策略可能只揭示了冰山一角。发表在的一项研究&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/why-discarded-brain-noise-matters-overlooked-networks-may-reshape-mental-health-treatment.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 00:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/why-discarded-brain-noise-matters-overlooked-networks-may-reshape-mental-health-treatment</guid></item><item><title>研究人员直接观察对μ子催化聚变至关重要的μ子分子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/researchers-directly-observe-muonic-molecules-critical-to-muon-catalyzed-fusion</link><description>科学家首次利用高分辨率X射线探测器直接观察到处于共振态的μ子分子&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-directly-observe-muonic-molecules-critical-to-muon-catalyzed-fusion2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 00:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/researchers-directly-observe-muonic-molecules-critical-to-muon-catalyzed-fusion</guid></item><item><title>FDG-PET 用于评估转移性乳腺癌初始治疗后的结果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/fdg-pet-for-estimating-outcomes-after-initial-treatment-for-metastatic-breast-cancer</link><description>在新诊断的转移性乳腺癌 (MBC) 患者中，一项临床队列试验使用 18F-氟脱氧葡萄糖正电子发射断层扫描 (FDG-PET) 与标准计算机断层扫描 (CT) 评估进行比较，评估了早期治疗反应。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/fdg-pet-for-estimating-outcomes-after-initial-treatment-for-metastatic-breast-cancer.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/fdg-pet-for-estimating-outcomes-after-initial-treatment-for-metastatic-breast-cancer</guid></item><item><title>音乐纠正大脑的“错误”预测</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/music-corrects-the-brains-glitched-predictions</link><description>音乐可以治疗精神病吗？一项新的研究揭示了歌曲创作如何帮助精神分裂症患者改善预测编码，减少偏执和社会孤立。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/music-corrects-the-brains-glitched-predictions.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/music-corrects-the-brains-glitched-predictions</guid></item><item><title>火星沙尘暴将水喷射到太空，科学家们感到震惊</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-stunned-as-mars-dust-storms-blast-water-into-space</link><description>今天的火星可能看起来像一片冰冻的沙漠，但新的证据表明，它水汪汪的过去并没有悄然消失——它可能是被强大的沙尘暴吹进太空的。科学家发现，即使是相对较小的局部风暴也能将水蒸气抛入高空，然后分解并逸出。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-stunned-as-mars-dust-storms-blast-water-into-space2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-stunned-as-mars-dust-storms-blast-water-into-space</guid></item><item><title>宇宙本身可能向我们隐藏了引力粒子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-universe-itself-might-be-hiding-the-gravity-particle-from-us</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-universe-itself-might-be-hiding-the-gravity-partic